Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Toilet-bound Hanako-kun"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Minamoto Kou!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, lame-ass traffic-safety earring!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, I heard a rumor and managed\Nto catch a ghost at the school entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks like a pushover and\Ndoesn't seem all that strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.29,0:02:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm gonna take care of his regrets\Nso he can rest in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that, but I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just 'cause I'm a cute ghost,\Nyou want to get rough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,--No, I--\N--Like in porn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,--Huh?! That's not--\N--Just like in porn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Apparition 8: Mitsuba"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Huff puff"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"Huff puff"\N"Tired out from insulting"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.58,0:02:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"Huff puff"\N"Tired out from insulting"\NA-Are you calmer now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.54,0:02:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't show weakness to an evil spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Minamoto Kou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the second son of\Nan ancient clan of exorcists.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.62,0:02:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Exorcists?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.91,0:02:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, you've been watching too much anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.91,0:02:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll annihilate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's an "exorcist" (LOL) with a lame-ass\Ntraffic-safety earring want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "Kou"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lame-ass traffic-safety earring pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"Whimper"\NLame-ass traffic-safety earring pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Whimper"\NDon't get rough with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me your name and regrets in\Nfive seconds or I'll just get rid of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What grade?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Silence"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What grade did you die in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Humph"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What are your regrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Photography! It's photography!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Photography?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say when you\Nask me my regrets out of nowhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but there was a photo I wanted\Nto take before I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're really going to help me\Ndo what I never got a chance to,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,then go get my camera.\NIt was donated to the photography club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mitsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you finish up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to stick with me\Nuntil I find the photo I wanted to take?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the great hereditary exorcist\NLame-ass Traffic-safety Earring
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,a lying pervert who breaks his promises\Nat the drop of a hat with a lame-ass traffic--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,--Don't get cocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,--I'll disappear! I'm gonna disappear!\N--Don't get cocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you've just been taking shots\Nof animals and landscapes and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What about people?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.91,0:04:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How about some shots of club activities?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's easier to win awards\Nfor photos of people, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the ultimate subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"Shock!"\NWhat's wrong with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take one already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, give back my camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you only take dirty photos anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That you, Kou?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yokoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:05:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... taking photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess you're up to something weird again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mitsuba"\NGuess you're up to something weird again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mitsuba"\NHey, that camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Mitsuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was sometime this winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear he died in some kind of accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He was in our class in first year, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he moved to a different class,\Nso I guess you wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Mitsuba Sousuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be sitting in name-order for a while,\Nso I'll be in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:05:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kou?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yokoo! Break time's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, better go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.37,0:06:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,--Mitsu--\N--I called out to everyone\NI thought was my friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,--I called out to everyone\NI thought was my friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but none of them recognized me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...I remembered them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's started raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I got bullied a lot in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:07:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I was "girly" or "cocky."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.37,0:07:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumb reasons like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you not act like that explains it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...because of that, I wanted to\Nstart junior high on the right foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I read the mood and acted friendly\Nso no one would call me cocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I got along casually with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a plain guy people barely notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get bullied,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but I didn't make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's why no one\Npays attention to me now that I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That rumor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're cocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You look girly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,--You're rude.\N--Hey--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're selfish. You're loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,--You're a camera geek.\N--Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gloomy sometimes, and you're a faker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone asks me what Mitsuba Sousuke\Nis like, that's what I'll say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.75,0:08:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for not noticing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You seemed so different from\Nfirst year that I didn't recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...maybe you shouldn't have forced yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I think you've got issues,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Minamoto-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were still alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:09:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,could we have been friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because you're dead
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean we can't be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I said quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,--You sure love sweets.\N--Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,--He who laughs at a sweet cries for a sweet!\N--Yeah! Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you shooting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.41,0:09:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that means a lot to me... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick with me until it develops tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm sure things will work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's pick this up tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll wait at the entr--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't have you running off on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving without even telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.08,0:10:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.91,0:10:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mitsuba,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you made a wish to me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.87,0:10:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,For everyone to remember you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're satisfied with just one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.79,0:10:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your hands off...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...my friend Mitsuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an apparition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I grant whoever summons me a wish\Nand take one thing in payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Amane grants wishes for\Nliving people in this life,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and I grant them for dead people in the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He wished, and I answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'll grant his wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A radio?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Mitsuba,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make your wish come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura, everything's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:11:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Broken Neck of the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a ghost with a broken neck\Nwho haunts the junior high entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a very lonely ghost,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,so he might try to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hey..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Have you forgotten me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't answer by saying his name,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...he'll break your neck\Nand make you just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The junior high entrance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,--No...\N--Have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it from a friend of a friend.\NAn accident in winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he'll break your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Minamoto... {\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Haku-joudai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure no one will forget about you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Broken Neck"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The Seven Wonders say they maintain\Nproper relations between humans and apparitions,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans and apparitions should\Njust be however they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If that would break the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,then it's better off broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuba, why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuba's wish was kind of vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't know what he\Nwanted to stay here to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but he didn't want it to end like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted everyone to remember him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With a vague wish, I could only\Nmake him into a half-baked apparition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But things are different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.83,0:14:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You drew out Mitsuba's real wish for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.79,0:14:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The stronger the wish, the regret,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the stronger and more definite\Nthe apparition can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuba's wish is:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"I want friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"I want to be with my friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"Forever and ever."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the crap and turn Mitsuba back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Besides, Mitsuba's regret\Nwas a photo he wanted to--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the more people's memories you stick in,\Nthe longer you can stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If that boy ends up like you,\Nyou can be together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you want,\Nor what you hurt to get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll forgive you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.91,0:15:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The price for your wish is "reason."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing left to get in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, struggle. Defy the world's design,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.91,0:16:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...get it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.70,0:17:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Amane!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How many years has it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.04,0:17:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten, twenty...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.87,0:17:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, we just saw each other\Non the roof the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I like the way people look\Nwhen they stop holding it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That time was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That time you killed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Amane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to play together, like we used to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mitsuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... you can turn him back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to normal. Like with\Nthe Misaki Stairs and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.62,0:18:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mitsuba I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.83,0:18:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuba Sousuke,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,is c-cocky,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,girly-looking,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,rude,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,selfish,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...and loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a camera geek,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,gloomy sometimes, a faker,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:19:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.75,0:19:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,death is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wandering the world of the living\Nas a spirit isn't a continuation of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When you die, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.83,0:19:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing new begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much you regret or wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,if you couldn't do something in life,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't do it after death, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how the world works.\NDefy that, and you end up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that you might be able
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.83,0:19:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,to sever his regrets,\Nhis attachment to the living world,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but it looks like it backfired.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be too kind to the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:19:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...no longer have futures.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-There has to be something more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Something I could have, should have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were strong like Teru-{\i1}nii{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,this would never have happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't blame yourself, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,For the dead, I'm sure annihilation\Nis the only salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This was for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Not one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.12,0:21:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"disappearing is the only salvation"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive him\Nfor doing that to Mitsuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.70,0:21:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako's probably right\Nthat the world has a system
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's nothing I can do to change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:22:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.04,0:22:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe the reason I was given the power
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.54,0:22:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to see and interfere with unearthly apparitions
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.20,0:22:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,is to do at least a little to turn\Nthat "nothing" into "something."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.45,0:22:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I still think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.00,0:22:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.45,0:22:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.83,0:22:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you shooting?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.75,0:22:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.20,0:22:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that means a lot to me... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.33,0:22:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.95,0:24:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Episode Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.45,0:24:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Tell me, Mitsuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}: Gossip"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.62,0:24:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Tell me, Mitsuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}: Gossip"\N"Were there any girls you liked?"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.33,0:24:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Tell me, Mitsuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}: Gossip"\N"Were there any girls you liked?"\N"Huh? Girls?"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.04,0:24:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Tell me, Mitsuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}: Gossip"\N"Were there any girls you liked?"\N"Huh? Girls?" "I don't think so."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.62,0:24:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I mean, I was cuter than all of them."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.00,0:24:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I mean, I was cuter than all of them."\N"Bam!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.33,0:24:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I mean, I was cuter than all of them."\N"Sparkle" "Bam!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.16,0:24:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I mean, I was cuter than all of them."\N"Sparkle" "Bam!"\N"Oh, okay..."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.50,0:24:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time:\NApparition 9: Tea Party"
